---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Developing Management Skills - ROM Business Psychology">

<!-- HERO WITH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative h-[50vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=1920&q=80"
    alt="Leadership development"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/90 via-blue-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">
      Teams
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-white text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      Developing<br/>Management Skills
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
      The challenge of leading people is more complex than ever. Traditional command-and-control approaches don't work anymoreâ€”we've translated modern leadership into habits that can be acquired.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUOTE BANNER -->
<section class="bg-slate-900 py-10">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <blockquote class="text-center">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-light italic">
        "People want to be led by honest and worthy individuals. They will not be motivated unless they understand why."
      </p>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BECOMING A LEADER -->
<section class="bg-white py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">The Journey</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Becoming a Leader</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We usually promote first-line managers from within the professional teams. The common practice states that in order to become a sales manager you should first be a salesman; before becoming R&D manager, you should work as an engineer.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Initial managerial legitimacy of young team leaders derives mainly from their professional expertise.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Yet, the promotion to a managerial position sets in motion a series of challenges. New leaders are obliged to rise to the occasion, sharpening their interpersonal and managerial skills.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Challenge</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Rise to the occasion</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Sharpen interpersonal skills</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Step outside comfort zone</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-600 rounded-full"></div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Develop managerial identity</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR OFFERING -->
<section class="bg-slate-50 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Solution</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Management Skills in a Nutshell</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-blue-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Needs Assessment</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Before kicking-off, we conduct a short needs assessment. We map gaps in knowledge, skills, and abilities, and assemble a tailormade training program.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-cyan-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Experiential Workshops</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          A series of workshops providing simple and concrete management practices, developing a "managerial language", and enhancing overall capacity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THREE CIRCLES -->
<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-[896px]">
    <div class="text-center text-white mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Three Management Circles</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our sessions cover three main management areas, providing practical tools for each level.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-white text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Self-Management</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>Gaining focus</li>
          <li>Managing priorities</li>
          <li>Planning</li>
          <li>Promoting infrastructure</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-white text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Team Management</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>Setting expectations</li>
          <li>Providing feedback</li>
          <li>Team building</li>
          <li>Conflict resolution</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-white text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Influencing Others</h3>
        <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>Impact on interfaces</li>
          <li>Increase collaboration</li>
          <li>Influence stakeholders</li>
          <li>Cross-functional leadership</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<Footer />
</Layout>
